        <Param val="~EGG HUNT~&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In this game, you and another player will aim to collect as many eggs as you can to earn points!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;On each round, both of you will start with 150 points. 10 points will be subtracted for every turn taken. The round will end once you or the other player collects an egg or both of you catch the chicken. You can collect an egg by moving to a tile with an egg. You can catch the chicken if you and the other player move to tile that are next to the chicken.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You and another player can move around to collect one of two eggs alone (worth 100 points) or cooperate to catch a chicken that can lay four eggs which will be split (worth 400 points total, or 200 points to each player). These points will be added to your total score on each round." valType="str" updates="constant" name="text"/>
