        <Param val="This time, both you and the other player collected an egg, which means that you both earned 100 points. You both started with 150 points, but took 1 turn (so you lost 10 points). In total, you both received 240 points.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Remember that either one of you will be able to collect an egg or both of you depending on how you play the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Press RIGHT ARROW to continue." valType="str" updates="constant" name="text"/>
